{"tid":683034,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先喺大快活食野 真係痴撚線 係痴撚哂線","createTime":"2018-05-29T11:01:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T11:15:54.000Z","uid":138458,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"733fc6aa2fe22538464e6936e9d9e93971975076","tid":683034,"uid":138458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T11:01:25.000Z","msg":"平時好小去大快活食野 啱啱見趕時間 買咗個砂礓雞飯 咁就有個圓形嘅野 你啲野食攞得就起勢咁震 咁我就攞翻埋位食 食緊嘅時候我聽到隔離對廢老夫婦嘅對話 真係o撚左<br />\n龜頭老公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  臭西雞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大快活阿姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喂阿姐 望咗你好耐 我啲野食擺咗出面先 點解你幫佢(其他人)攞先 唔係我嗰個先<br />\n<br />\n當時已經呆撚左 佢地都唔係坐好耐就已經屌鬼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Sorry 你嗰個仲未齊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁到未齊？ <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係呀差個菜 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁你下次應該跟翻先後攞我嗰個先 你部機冇用<br />\n<br />\n我心諗你有手有腳 啲野食正正係隔離你都唔攞 其次想問各位巴打喺大快活係咪應該自己攞定係好似嗰廢老咁？<br />\n我記得對上幾次食都係有部機 自己出去攞 未見過有人要個阿姐去攞   但今次見到有唔少中坑廢老睇撚住報紙 部機已經震緊 都唔出去攞 係要人幫你  <br />\n係咪我問題<br />\n利申 廢老區"},{"pid":"1254081c033ff523a7c18c397b22ce4df0587a8a","tid":683034,"uid":138458,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T11:06:45.000Z","msg":"係度勸大家 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n如非必要<br />\n咪撚做飲食業</span></span>"},{"pid":"3aab2eb88b36e715fb3154cc604a46dfdb1720ad","tid":683034,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T11:07:28.000Z","msg":"大把"},{"pid":"8554235f4b2095801f3115a2bae47f5db26cc5bf","tid":683034,"uid":54223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T11:07:55.000Z","msg":"入黎仲想睇雞胸飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e24c669958f578bc6eba1b457d476aa9ac6c6977","tid":683034,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1254081c033ff523a7c18c397b22ce4df0587a8a","tid":683034,"uid":138458,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T11:06:45.000Z","msg":"係度勸大家 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n如非必要<br />\n咪撚做飲食業</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T11:09:03.000Z","msg":"幫口屌鳩佢呀嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d701c260df5ce92cf8d9bf55a60b52eaf8aad0df","tid":683034,"uid":36894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T11:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79bea59fe24d6a66f3c071fca7aa7d06b68f28d9","tid":683034,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T11:15:54.000Z","msg":"好似係送餐服務嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/654258/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/654258/1</a>"}]}